"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/1k9DgxgrCqbNlDfxI_57j.png?height=305&width=1146)\\n\\nAs part of our drive to [decentralise](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/Bz8plTeNzVaYGOvJ7utPNUn41k6G4HSh3fnhOxzWjb8) Email is now optional. However, official communications with venues or associates must be via an @mundolingo.org Email. Here’s how to do it.\\n\\n## Terms of use\\n\\n### Personalised Emails\\n\\nPersonally addressed Emails (“Dear James…”) stay in the inbox until responded. Once responded it’s saved to a sub-folder (not deleted).\\n\\n### Non-personalised Emails\\n\\nNon-personal Emails (“Hi”, “Dear sir/madam”) can be deleted.\\n\\n### Clear your Emails\\n\\nNothing says “unprofessional” like not responding an Email until a week later. Keep your inbox clear so you can engage new emails quickly.\\n\\n### Too much SPAM?\\n\\nLet the Tech Lead know, we may be able to improve your spam filter.\\n\\n### Your Quota (150MB)\\n\\nEach inbox quota is 150mb. If you reach your quota, try this:\\n\\n* Find Emails with attachments such as images, files or videos and delete them.\\n* If you have many Emails over 3 years old, you could delete these.\\n* **Deleted emails go to your Trash Bin** and this counts towards your quota; empty your trash bin.\\n\\n## Email Setup\\n\\nYou need an email client such as Microsoft Outlook or [Mozilla Thunderbird](https://www.thunderbird.net/) (Free).Here we show a setup in Outlook but the steps are similar whichever program you use.\\n\\n### Step 1:\\n\\nSelect **File** > **Add Account**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ixizmptAHnrRocW1GNzeH.png?height=396&width=820)\\n\\n### Step 2:\\n\\nSelect **Manually configure server settings** > **Next**\\n\\n![It may look different or be worded differently on your system](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/YxpNXUQKykKscOaGOxAgo.png?height=478&width=687)\\n\\n### Step 3:\\n\\nSelect **Internet E-mail** (POP or IMAP) > **Next**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/lnPX8zbuEKJB5pIqcF-bx.png?height=478&width=687)\\n\\n### Step 4:\\n\\n**Replace:** “yourcity” with your city’s name\\n**Replace:** “yourmail” with the email provided by your Tech Lead\\n**Enter:** password provided by your Tech Lead\\n\\nClick “**More Settings…**”\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/GCI_8D6xGjTyLw3ayTjcH.png?height=478&width=687)\\n\\n### Step 5:\\n\\nFill in the following details replacing **YOURCITY** with your assigned email address:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/11WNv14kddkdfrSRLlf3E.png?height=501&width=903)\\n\\n### Step 6:\\n\\nSelect “**Advanced**”\\n\\nSelect “**SLL**” for both Incoming and Outgoing and then the port numbers 993 and 465.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/On2O7tS1W-pj647xvKq6N.png?height=470&width=712)\\n\\nClick **Ok**. If all is well, it will do this:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_XF1wdcAK-4ApPeWa5atZ.png?height=708&width=774)\\n\\n## Signature\\n\\nPlease set up your signature so that it’s automatically added to all of your Emails. It should look like this:\\n\\n**\\\\[Name\\\\] \\\\[Surname\\\\] |** Manager\\n**MundoLingo**.org\\n\\n## Folder Structure\\n\\nMake a folder for each group of people you’re likely to receive emails from. For example: **Inquiries, Venues, Associates, local print shops** etc. It will help you later\",\"timestamp\":1637321204,\"title\":\"EOM | Email \"},\"digest\":\"4MOW683fmTUUjHmlDF1HHMqYhCQtzecW8x-Q3SKx7lY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"F8zG1zTeZMDpV2_EIlWrsKpmnGDh3SxjOF71ivpgrJg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cTaiHvTF70f6CzGg3oqJ4Z5azdotT-0kGnHltBTC7IE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"jTXAkpUrYIR1mnUb1jJ0gs_DerIEcn28NI-KM9u-z23NKOyffFzk7HqbmzjAndGUgoTDSQ0tNOwqNFDsKGmAtg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9ffe03abbb74481883195e9c49f74ad3362bbcc9be4787bc7d86b31ee0a27a51494508e5274ca44c64dfc0a67507f0b6354439a75b1d7c337ff95a9f16a6c4c11b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"F8zG1zTeZMDpV2_EIlWrsKpmnGDh3SxjOF71ivpgrJg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cTaiHvTF70f6CzGg3oqJ4Z5azdotT-0kGnHltBTC7IE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"C6xC0RpDtCoFOc6atGcC5dMtvfXBBLcnOe_xS3KyeFs\"}"